Invocation Name: number game
des:
Guess a number, and Alexa will tell you if you need to guess higher or lower. Alexa will also tell you how many times you have played before

HOW TO PLAY:

Say, "Alexa, open number game" to open the skill
Say a number, and Alexa will determine if it is too high or low!
IF you guess correctly, you win! Also it will tell you how many guesses you took to win

have fun!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
